                           'KouQuad' 1.0

                        by Charles-N. Jacob

  'KouQuad' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to rotate 'Quads'
-large tiles containing 4 smaller coloured tiles- so that tiles of
the same colour are placed next to each other. The more tiles of
the same colour there are, the more points you get.

  When it is not possible to place coloured tiles together, you can
click on the 'fall-and-move-left' button to regroup all remaining
coloured tiles together.

  Have fun!

